    "By multiplying the normalized weight matrix with the value matrix, the model constructs the attention matrix.",
    "As a result, the ESM2 650M model was able to accurately predict the deepest GO term, RNA processing.",
    "RNA processing is a key step in biomolecular processes that involves the conversion of preliminarily transcribed RNA into mature RNA molecules, a process that plays a decisive role in the precise regulation of gene expression.",
    "The Diamond method based on sequence similarity encountered challenges in predicting the function of the Q9BZE2 protein due to the failure to find sequences homologous to the Q9BZE2 protein in the training set.",
